title: Brighton and Hove Albion vs Newcastle United - English Premier League 2024/2025
description: Newcastle are winless in all seven of their away Premier League games against Brighton, the joint-most they have visited an opponent in the competition without ever winning. It’s the outright most Brighton have faced a side without losing at home in the Premier League. Following their 1-0 win in October, Brighton could complete their third league double over Newcastle, after 1978-79 and 2020-21.

title: Chelsea vs Liverpool - English Premier League 2024/2025
description: Chelsea are winless in their last 10 meetings with Liverpool in all competitions, only once before going longer without a win over the Reds. After their 2-1 win in October, Liverpool are looking to complete their first league double over Chelsea since their title-winning 2019-20 campaign. Arne Slot could become only the third Reds boss to win both of his first two league games against Chelsea in charge of the club, after Bill Shankly and Roy Evans.

title: PSG vs Arsenal - UEFA Champions League 2024/25 Semi Finals - 2nd Leg
description: PSG’s 1-0 win the first leg was their first ever victory in six attempts against Arsenal. Both of their home games against the Gunners have finished 1-1. Having been unbeaten in their first 13 away games against French sides in all competitions, Arsenal have now lost their last two visits against Rennes in 2019 and Lens in 2023.

title: La Liga ELCLÁSICO, THE MOVIE EP1
description: Kylian Mbappe and Lamine Yamal were the stars of the first LALIGA EA Sports ElClásico of the season. The former, a new signing for Real Madrid, was making his first appearance in this showcase fixture. And the latter was leading FC Barcelona after triumphing at the summers European Championship. The ElClásico film delves into the careers of both players, revealing their origins and their lives off the pitch, and follows their performances in detail during LALIGAs most anticipated football event.

title: Internazionale vs Barcelona - UEFA Champions League 2024/25 Semi Finals - 2nd Leg
description: This will be the 18th major European meeting between Internazionale and Barcelona, with only Bayern Munich vs Real Madrid, Juventus vs Real Madrid and Inter vs Real Madrid played more often in history. Each of the last two games between the teams have ended 3-3, in the UEFA Champions League in October 2022 and this season’s first leg. Barcelona have won just one of their six away UEFA Champions League matches against Internazionale, a 2-1 win in December 2019. Overall, Barca have managed just five wins in 24 away games in Italy, their lowest win ratio in any non-Spanish nation in the competition.

title: Bodø / Glimt vs Tottenham Hotspur - UEFA Europa League 2024/25 - Sime Finals 2nd Leg
description: In the history of the UEFA Europa League since its rebrand ahead of the 2009-10 season, there have been 92 instances of a side winning the first leg of a knockout match on home soil by a 2+ goal margin, of which only nine have failed to progress in the overall tie. All eight prior semi-finalists to achieve the feat have progressed to the final. Across their major European history, Bodø/Glimt have lost all four of their matches against English opposition, including their only one on home soil vs Arsenal in October 2022. Each of the other three defeats have seen the Norwegian side concede exactly three goals.

title: Bodø / Glimt vs Tottenham Hotspur - UEFA Europa League 2024/25 - Sime Finals 2nd Leg
description: In the history of the UEFA Europa League since its rebrand ahead of the 2009-10 season, there have been 92 instances of a side winning the first leg of a knockout match on home soil by a 2+ goal margin, of which only nine have failed to progress in the overall tie. All eight prior semi-finalists to achieve the feat have progressed to the final. Across their major European history, Bodø/Glimt have lost all four of their matches against English opposition, including their only one on home soil vs Arsenal in October 2022. Each of the other three defeats have seen the Norwegian side concede exactly three goals.

title: Bundesliga Highlights 2024/25 Week 32
description: Each Bundesliga Matchweek is condensed into a 52-minute highlights show. Every game, goal, penalty, red card and everything in between is squeezed into an action-packed hour to ensure no football fan misses a kick across the game season.

title: St. Pauli vs Stuttgart - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 32
description: VfB Stuttgart lost 1-0 against FC St. Pauli in the first half of the season, bringing an end to their 10-game unbeaten run against the Kiezkicker in all competitions. St. Pauli could now go unbeaten against the Swabians across an entire Bundesliga season and record back-to-back top-flight wins against them for the first time. VfB Stuttgart have only won one of their last 10 Bundesliga games. The Swabians have 41 points from 31 games, meaning they are 23 points worse off compared to this stage last season – no other club has suffered such a big drop-off compared to 2023/24.

title: Borussia Monchengladbach vs Hoffenheim - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 32
description: Borussia Monchengladbach have won five of their last six Bundesliga games against TSG Hoffenheim. The Foals are currently on a three-game winning streak at home against Hoffenheim for the first time, while they have also scored in all 16 top-flight home matches against TSG. Borussia Monchengladbach are without a win in four consecutive Bundesliga games for the first time this season and are the only team in the league to lose each of their last three matches. The Foals also started 2025 with three straight defeats but haven’t suffered four in a row since November/December 2021.

title: Union Berlin vs Werder Bremen - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 32
description: After a 2-1 victory on their first trip to Union Berlin in the Bundesliga in September 2019, Werder Bremen have since lost their last three away games against them. Of teams that Werder have played multiple times away from home in the top flight, they only have a higher loss percentage at RB Leipzig than at Union. 1. FC Union Berlin are currently on the longest unbeaten run of all Bundesliga teams – FCU have only gone longer without defeat in the top flight between April and September 2022. SV Werder Bremen haven’t lost any of their last five league games, with only FC Bayern, Bayer 04 Leverkusen and Union currently on longer unbeaten runs.

title: Augsburg vs Holstein Kiel - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 32
description: Holstein Kiel’s 5-1 win over FC Augsburg in the first half of this season is their biggest-ever victory in the Bundesliga. FCA have won four of their last six home games against promoted sides, having previously been winless in their last 15 top-flight home fixtures against promoted teams. Since the 5-1 defeat in Kiel, FC Augsburg have conceded just 10 goals in 16 Bundesliga games – a league low in 2025. Holstein Kiel have shipped a league-high 36 goals this calendar year and also have the worst defence in the division overall.

title: My Faith in Sport -Sawm
description: Ramadan is a crucial period in the Islamic calendar but fasting (Sawm) can provide complications for athletes who are trying to compete at the highest level. But to what extent is fasting a negative or can it actually aid performance? We look at the life and adaptation throughout Ramadan of Adam Azim – an unbeaten professional boxer from the UK, Fares El Bakh – a weightlifter who won Qatar’s first ever Olympic gold medal, and Zainab Alema – a rugby player who is aiming to become the first player to represent England wearing a hijab.Experts in Sports Science and Nutrition from Aspetar Clinic, Qatar also add detail of the physical impact athletes encounter during Ramadan

title: Al Ahli (KSA) vs Kawasaki (JPN) - AFC Champions League Elite 2024/25 - Final
description: Al-Ahli will face Kawasaki Frontale for the first time in the AFC Champions League elite and for the first time against a Japanese team. Conversely, this will be Kawasaki Frontales second encounter against a Saudi team after defeating Al-Nassr 3-2 in the semi-finals. Al-Ahli have won only once in 5 matches against East Asian teams, with the win against Shenzhen 2-1 in the 2005 quarter-finals. This will be the fourth final between a Saudi team and a Japanese team in the AFC Champions League elite, the most common final matchup in the tournament. All previous finals were between Al-Hilal and Urawa Red Diamonds, with Al-Hilal winning one title in 2019 and Urawa winning two titles in 2017 and 2

title: My Faith in Sport - Sawm
description: Ramadan is a crucial period in the Islamic calendar but fasting (Sawm) can provide complications for athletes who are trying to compete at the highest level. But to what extent is fasting a negative or can it actually aid performance? We look at the life and adaptation throughout Ramadan of Adam Azim – an unbeaten professional boxer from the UK, Fares El Bakh – a weightlifter who won Qatar’s first ever Olympic gold medal, and Zainab Alema – a rugby player who is aiming to become the first player to represent England wearing a hijab. Experts in Sports Science and Nutrition from Aspetar Clinic, Qatar also add detail of the physical impact athletes encounter during Ramadan.

title: Tremblay vs St Raphael - LNH Division 1 - French Handball Starligue
description: Dive into the excitement of French handball with Liqui Moly Starligue, formerly LNH Division 1. Established in 1952, this premier league event features 16 top teams battling for glory. With Montpellier’s 14 Handball titles and Paris Saint-Germains 11 wins, the competition is fierce. Champions earn spots in the EHF Champions League, while cup winners qualify for the European League.

description: Meet the Coton de Tulear, Great Pyrenees, Chiweenie, English Setter, Pug and American Eskimo, and find out which dogs make the best travelling companions?

description: Sustainable Future is CNBCs umbrella franchise to house explorations and discussions on the most important issue of our time; sustainability.

title: We Baby Bears: Worlds Apart Episode 1: Blarfenpleepo; Worlds
description: Grizzly, Panda and Ice embark on a journey to find a place to settle down.

title: Jellystone!: Cindy vs Noodle Arms; Hot Guys, Cold Turkey
description: The lovable residents of Jellystone get into all sorts of wacky misadventures.

title: The Tom and Jerry Show: Someones in the Kitchen with Mynah; Dental C
description: Arch-rivals Tom and Jerry constantly try to one up each other.

title: Tiny Toons Looniversity: Freshman Orientoontion
description: Buster and Babs Bunny, Sweetie Bird and other characters enroll in the Acme Looniversity.

title: Alaskan Bush People: Driving Miss Rainy
description: While youngest Brown brother Noah stays behind to continue repairs to Browntown, the other eight members of the wolfpack take on their riskiest haul ever.

title: Alaskan Bush People: Winter Watch
description: Patriarch Billy sees an opportunity to tie up loose ends, connect with the bush and keep the wolfpack close with a family visit to the winter watch of Excursion Inlet.

title: Expedition Unknown: Revealing The Triangle
description: To conclude his epic investigation, Josh Gates uses cutting-edge technology to investigate the Bermuda Triangles most infamous shipwreck and lost flights.

title: Ant Anstead Master Mechanic: O Motor Where Art Thou
description: Ants engine for the Alfa 158 is still missing in action and he is losing patience. Hes been working early mornings, late nights and weekends.

title: Wheeler Dealers: Ford Mustang Mach 1
description: Car dealer Mike Brewer snatches up a 1973 Ford Mustang Mach 1. Can mechanic Ant Anstead bring back the lost power by tuning up and enhancing the engine?

title: Wheeler Dealers: Saab 96
description: Mike Brewer and Ant Anstead try to arouse the passion of the Saab enthusiast community by restoring a rusty, non-driving 1973 Saab 96 to its past glory.

title: Outback Opal Hunters: Episode 11
description: The Mooka Boys risk being buried alive as they hunt for a legendary mine shaft. The Blacklighters are overwhelmed by choking dust on their bone-dry claim.

title: Street Outlaws: Fastest in America: KY Vs. WY Grudge Night
description: The racers set up a fresh batch of grudge matches. Everyones on edge when theres a nasty crash in a race between teams Texas and California.

title: Gold Rush: White Water: Between Craziness And Insanity
description: Deep in a remote Alaskan canyon, Gold Rush veterans Fred and Dustin Hurt are back searching for gold. But this time, their lives are on the line.

title: Gold Rush: White Water: First Gold
description: In the remote Chilkat Mountains, Fred and Dustin Hurt are on a treasure hunt for Alaskas unfound gold deposits. Will they find the first flakes of white water gold?

title: Roadworthy Rescues: Bandit Chevy
description: Derek finds a 1951 Chevy Deluxe thats been sitting for 44 years. He needs to get it running and stopping if he hopes to tackle the Chattanooga hills and make it home.

title: Salvage Hunters: The Restorers: Civil War Boots
description: Metalworker Ted works his magic on a rusty old mining cart. Martin restores a pair of Civil War era military boots, and Steve and Gill save a broken antique table.

title: Salvage Hunters: Classic Cars: VW Fastback Type 3 And Rover P6
description: Drew and Paul are in Somerset to hunt down a 1970s VW Type 3 Fastback. And, they revamp a Rover P6 built at the height of the British Leyland crisis.

title: Treehouse Masters: Triple Decker Record Setter
description: Pete is in Louisiana to take on his biggest treehouse ever. Totalling 1200 square feet, it will comprise of three separate levels and a 70 foot bridge.

title: Treehouse Masters: International: Germany
description: Pete joins two renowned treehouse builders - Christopher Richter and Andreas Wenning - as they tour Deutschland and every treehouse they can find.

title: Kindig Customs: Lets Make Green Great Again
description: After some intense development, the client is happy with the shade of green Dave has concocted. But will he fall for it when he sees it in on the car?

title: Kindig Customs: Easy Does It
description: A returning client is back with another classic, a 1965 Mustang Fastback. He likes to keep a stock look, but with updated drivetrain and modern amenities.

title: Gem Hunters Down Under: Necessity Is The Mother Of...
description: Ray takes on the job of bashing and sawing through his biggest rough stones. The Bushies reckon theyve finally hit payday. But is it wishful thinking?

title: Gem Hunters Down Under: The End Of The Road
description: Anthony goes back to school, learning to cut gems, while Jodie enjoys the peace as she digs alone. The Richardsons dig deep at the old Rabbi Claim.

title: Gold Rush: White Water: Groundbreaking Gold
description: Fred opens the door to a new site. After a bust-up with Fred, Kayla makes a discovery that will change the course of their entire season.

title: Gold Rush: White Water: Boiling Point
description: Fred celebrates his 78th birthday by diving for gold. Kaylas crew is on a hot streak, but their luck runs out as tensions between crew members reach a boiling point.

title: Deadliest Catch: Wheelhouse Bound
description: Sig gets tough news at sea, forcing the Hansens to make a critical decision. Meanwhile, Jacob reaches a stalemate with Keith on the Wizard.

title: Deadliest Catch: Amazing Grace
description: Sig buries his beloved mother and the last of his familys pioneering generation. Plus, Sean Dwyer sees trouble in a new partner.

title: Outback Opal Hunters: Water You Waiting For?
description: With water running critically low at their only wash dam, The Cheals work to restore a second agitator. Slim Pickings battle a bung wall breach.

title: Wheeler Dealers World Tour: 2CV Fourgonnette - France
description: In Southern France, Mike and Elvis find a charming 2CV Fourgonnette. It’s got a modest engine, tired suspension and missing rear seats.

title: Salvage Hunters: The Restorers: Settle Down
description: French polisher Alex is challenged to rescue a settle bed. James restores a Ms. Pac-Man arcade machine, while Ted works on two weathered chairs.

title: How Do They Do It?: Super Yachts, Space Suits
description: How does a Dutch company make the worlds fastest superyachts? And, how do they make new space suits that weigh and cost the fifth of the previous design?

title: How Do They Do It?: Parma Ham, Underground Signs
description: How is Parma ham, the most famous ham in the world, made? Plus, how do they make rowing machines, and how are the iconic London Underground signs made?

title: Expedition X: Secrets Of The Nazi Occult
description: Phil and Heather visit a castle reportedly built over a Nazi portal to hell. The team seeks proof of sinister activity beneath the castles chapel.

title: 100 Days Wild: Rogue Rage
description: Under pressure to catch a moose, Andrew and Gerrid must also contend with Olivers stubbornness. Plus, Adam works on different building projects for the base camp.

title: Marooned with Ed Stafford: Patagonia
description: Dropped in the foothills of the Andes in Argentine Patagonia, Ed faces extreme exposure to both intense sunlight and freezing temperatures, eating tadpoles and ant eggs.

title: Alaskan Bush People: Growing The Wolfpack
description: An early spring lets the family to make progress on unfinished business. But a visitor from Billys past threatens to undermine the future of Browntown.

title: Alaskan Bush People: High Tide Housing
description: An unexpected visit from the mayor of a nearby island may forever change the face of Browntown. And an opportunity for strong man Gabe comes with serious risks.

title: Expedition Unknown: The Secret Solved
description: One of the puzzles of The Secret, a case Josh Gates has been chasing for years, might have been solved. Will the solution be in his hometown?

title: Ant Anstead Master Mechanic: Rise And Wine
description: Ant tries to sweet-talk his way into taking the completed Alfa 158 to the US Grand Prix in Austin. But the car isnt done, and the crew must do the heavy lifting.

title: Wheeler Dealers: Mitsubishi 3000GT VR-4
description: Mike tries to tap into the 90s nostalgia scene with a 1994 Mitsubishi 3000GT VR-4. Ant has his work cut out for him returning the car to its original state.

title: Wheeler Dealers: Ford Ranchero
description: Mike and Ant work on one of the first utility vehicles, a 64 Falcon Ranchero. Its vintage features are suffering under a coat of cheap black paint.

title: Outback Opal Hunters: Episode 12
description: Scotty gets lost while exploring hidden tunnels on the Bishops massive claim. Jack and Mickey are nearly crushed as the Tarantos try to move their machinery.

title: Street Outlaws: Fastest in America: Iowa Vs Utah PT 1
description: Teams Utah and Iowa face off in the final matchup of the Wildcard Round. Utah lack inexperience - but will they prove theyre a force to be reckoned with?

title: Gold Rush: White Water: Dredge Down
description: The first gold nugget promises a monster payday. But when Dustin dives a torrent where the current moves rocks, a rogue boulder almost costs him his life.

title: Gold Rush: White Water: Boulder Battles
description: Freds ex-boss Todd Hoffman has invested $50,000 in the Dakota Boys operation. He infuriates Dustin when he pays a surprise visit to a chopper.

title: Roadworthy Rescues: Termite Tempest
description: Derek saves a 1966 Pontiac Tempest with a rare overhead-camshaft six-cylinder engine, working magic on the upholstery and converting the OHC to EFI.

title: Salvage Hunters: The Restorers: Dazzling Peacock Head
description: Julia restores a broken peacock head from a festival float for dealer Natasha. Plus, Steve rescues a pair of worn antique tables from a Suffolk stately home.

title: Salvage Hunters: Classic Cars: MGC And BMW 635
description: In Hampshire Drew and Paul uncover a rare 1960s MGC, but clash over how to restyle it. And, in Dorset, they fall for an 80s BMW 635 Coupe left in a barn for 15 years.

title: Treehouse Masters: High Noon Saloon
description: Pete saddles up to build a wild-west themed treehouse. Set in a lone Douglas Fir on the range, Pete builds a structure with a county jail loft and copper ceiling.

title: Building Off The Grid: Ohio Valley Hut
description: Two brothers are building a high-end, off-grid vacation home in the middle of their 2,000-acre cattle ranch. They only have four months to complete it.

title: Kindig Customs: Thank You For Your Service
description: An active-duty serviceman wants to get his 51 Ford pickup finished once and for all. They get to work stretching the cab and redesigning the front end.

title: Kindig Customs: Unfinished Business
description: The 51 Ford pickup is ready for final assembly. But the team hit problems prepping it for a serviceman who is returning from a year away in a war zone.

title: Gem Hunters Down Under: Beyond The Boulder
description: Old Timers Ray and Paul return to where they removed a huge boulder to see if its hiding gems. Gemfield newcomers Matt and Amber hunt down sapphires.

title: Gem Hunters Down Under: Operation Washplant
description: Old Timer Ray has another claim, but drilling a hole brings its own set of problems. Plus, Michael and Cheries claim isnt producing enough sapphires.

title: Gold Rush: White Water: Gamblin Man
description: In a bid to rescue his season, Dustin plans a daring double dive to get gold. Meanwhile, Kaylas crew struggles to adapt after losing a crew member.

title: Gold Rush: White Water: Hard Times At House Rock
description: In an act of sheer desperation, Dustin Hurt gambles his entire future on a dangerous mining strategy. Will the risk lead to reward or ruin?

title: Deadliest Catch: Bering Sea Superstition
description: A new deckhand falls ill on the Time Bandit, raising questions for Andy. Captain Rick deals with a severe crew injury and Wild Bills plan A fails.

title: Deadliest Catch: In Need Of Rescue
description: Sig returns from his mothers funeral only to find his gear in harms way. The Coast Guard gets a call to extract a sailor with broken legs 200 miles out to sea.

title: Outback Opal Hunters: Glitch In The Matrix
description: In the race to meet a rainbow matrix order ahead of the Lightning Ridge Opal Festival, The Misfits bet everything on untested DIY contraptions.

title: Wheeler Dealers World Tour: Ford XR8 - Australia
description: Mike and Elvis engage in the ultimate Aussie showdown: Ford versus Holden. Can their Ford XR8 outpace the Holden GTS at the Mount Panorama circuit?

title: Salvage Hunters: The Restorers: Pedigree Pooches
description: Sculptor Nick is tasked with transforming a pair of headless garden ornaments. And, Drew asks leather restorer Martin to revamp an Avro Anson chair.

title: How Do They Do It?: Barra Airport, Lederhosen
description: How do planes take off and land on a beach at one of the worlds oldest airports? And, how do they hand-make the national dress of Bavaria, lederhosen?

title: How Do They Do It?: Lobster Fishing
description: How do they catch the worlds largest lobsters? How do they build the iconic chesterfield sofa? And, how do they capture the worlds sharpest TV pictures?

title: Shortys Dream Shop: Training Day Lowrider
description: A big fan of "Training Day" wants his 78 Monte Carlo built in the same vein, with a swapped LS, beefed-up brakes and suspension, and a new interior.

title: Kindig Customs: New Engine, New Headache
description: While not the most popular model, the Fox Body Mustang is actually making a comeback, and the one that rolls into the shop needs a lot of love.

title: Wheeler Dealers: Saab 900
description: Mike thinks theres money to be made on a soft-top Saab 900, but with a dicey clutch and woolly steering, Elvis has concerns. Can they get it back to its best?

title: Alaskan Bush People: Shots In The Dark
description: The wolfpack is on high alert after mysterious shots were fired causing property damage on the shores. Plus, the family must finish a salvage job shorthanded.

title: Alaskan Bush People: Judgement Day
description: The Browns are busy making the most of spring by hunting and building improvements. But in just 72 hours they are forced to leave the bush for an unknown fate.

title: Expedition Unknown: The Warrior Queens Treasure
description: Josh Gates searches across England to unearth a cache of ancient treasures belonging to the legendary Celtic queen, Boudica.

title: Ant Anstead Master Mechanic: License To Grille
description: Ants ambitious Alfa build is on the home stretch, but his new baby is due any day. And, he gets good news about his plan to unveil the car at the US Grand Prix.

title: Wheeler Dealers: Dodge A100 Van
description: Mike picks up an extremely distressed 1965 Dodge A-100 Sportsman. Will custom-built surf inspired details provide enough wow-factor to snag a buyer?

title: Wheeler Dealers: Austin-Healey
description: Mike Brewer and Ant Anstead are bringing to auction a highly desirable 1965 Austin-Healey 3000 MkIII. Will a sparkling new interior be enough to earn top dollar?

title: Outback Opal Hunters: Episode 13
description: The Bushmen attempt drilling for the first time with a 50-year-old exploration rig. Plus, the Mooka Boys go on a treasure hunt in a scorpion-riddled mine.

title: Street Outlaws: Fastest in America: Iowa vs. Utah Pt 2
description: The matchup between Utah and Iowa continues. The teams are tied up as they head into the second round of their Wildcard matchup.

title: Kindig Customs: Restorations? Were Talking Bout Restorations?
description: Dave takes on a restoration for clients celebrating their 25th anniversary. Theyve owned the car since they got married.

title: Kindig Customs: Its A Barn Door Deluxe, Of Course
description: Dave has done double-cab VWs, Bugs, and Karmann Ghias, but now he is taking on something completely different - and even more rare.

title: Kindig Customs: The Big Brother
description: The crew matches the two-tone paint job on the 53 Barn Door Deluxe build. They add a custom trim, a new engine, 22 windows and a custom interior.

title: Kindig Customs: Who Gets Number One?
description: Dave and the crew proved they could execute Daves production Corvette vision. But now that some have sold, they have to get them completely finished.

title: Wheeler Dealers: VW Split-Screen
description: Mike wants to splash the cash on a custom bus but Edd favours a more conservative campervan. Edd is an air-cooled expert but will this strategy pay dividends?

title: Wheeler Dealers: BMW Z1
description: Mike is on the lookout for a two-seat roadster with attitude in the form of the original BMW Z1. This zippy sports car could make a tidy profit when Edd gets stuck in.

title: Wheeler Dealers: Veteran Car
description: To celebrate their 100th car Mike and Edd restore a Darracq Type L. Will they be ready in time to face their toughest ever test drive - the London to Brighton Run?

title: Homestead Rescue: A Golden Opportunity
description: The Raneys convert an old barn into a commercial fishing kitchen. But when Marty is forced to quarantine, Matt and Misty make a golden discovery.

title: Feds: Kidnapped
description: A kidnapping brings FBI agents to Illinois in a race against time to find Larry and Connie Van Oosten. The truth shocks the town as agents try to find the couple alive.

title: Project Impossible: Man v Nature
description: A new breed of tools allows man to face deadly forces once thought impossible. On this episode: a polar survival suit, a thermal imaging fire fighter mask, and a big wave surfing emergency vest.

title: Lost Worlds: Ivan The Terrible
description: Russias first Tsar led a brutal and unpredictable life. Follow the story of the fortification and expansion of his nation.

title: Monsterquest: The Real Cujo
description: A team searches for feral dogs to uncover where they live and determine how dangerous they are in the wake of reports of predatory packs of canines attacking people.

title: Digging For The Truth: Search For El Dorado
description: Intrepid host Josh Bernstein goes in search of the legendary lost City of Gold. From the peaks of the Andes to the depths of the Amazon, can he find the truth?

title: The Universe: Supernovas
description: Jets of high-energy light are propelled into space and can emit intense radiation for years. Astronomers believe this creates the building blocks of planets, people and plants. The Supernova hunters look at recorded supernovas throughout time.

title: Ancient Aliens: The Hidden Empire
description: Explores the controversial theory that extraterrestrials have visited Earth. From the age of the dinosaurs to ancient Egypt.

title: Missing In Alaska: It Lurks Beneath The Ice
description: Recent sightings around Alaska match native stories of a vicious Arctic mermaid that attacks unsuspecting people. With only five per cent of the worlds oceans explored, could a sinister mermaid be among the oceans undocumented creatures?

title: Lost Gold Of World War II: What Lies Beneath
description: The team triggers a possible water trap in the cave and are forced to stop digging. Martin Flagg believes the Story Rock indicates a tunnel behind a waterfall and the team brings in a Navy diver to explore the plunge pools and search for an entrance.

description: Aphrodisias is a city of marble, dedicated to the goddess of beauty: Aphrodite. Discover how the city was forgotten and then found again in the mid-20th century.

description: MonsterQuest goes to Mexico to investigate the phenomena of Unidentified Flying Humanoids.

title: Digging For The Truth: Nefertiti: The Mummy Returns
description: Queen Nefertiti was once the most beautiful and powerful woman in Egypt - renowned in the ancient world. But she vanished without a trace, lost to the sands of Egypt for more than three thousand years.

title: The Universe: Space Travel
description: Is space warp-drive technology possible? Discover the array of spacecraft being designed which could see man travel through the final frontier.

title: Ancient Aliens: Space Station Moon
description: Explores the controversial theory that extraterrestrials have visited Earth. From the age of the dinosaurs to ancient Egypt.

title: Brad Meltzers Lost History: D-Day Footage
description: The team join the hunt for lost footage of a D-Day secret mission. Plus, can they find one of The Beatles, George Harrisons most famous guitars?

title: Chasing Mummies: Buried
description: Deep in the Egyptian sand, Zahi make the extraordinary discovery of five intact burials and, just as he thinks things couldnt get any better, he unearths a brutally murdered mummy.

title: Secret History Of Humans: Building Earth
description: Inspired by the divine, we create monuments to its power (Stonehenge, the Great Pyramid). New challenges create new sciences, and when the Romans mixed volcanic ash with water they created a new super-material: concrete.

title: Secret History Of Humans: Need For Speed
description: No prizes for second place! In this episode we learn how being the fastest enabled empires to be born and capitalism to thrive.

description: MonsterQuest looks into reports of chimpanzees on the loose in the United States.

title: Digging For The Truth: Pompeii: Secrets Revealed
description: In 79 AD, the mighty volcano Vesuvius exploded in one of the most deadly eruptions of all time, burying the city of Pompeii and other Roman towns along the Bay of Naples beneath layers of ash and pumice.

title: The Universe: Constellations
description: A useful tool for astronomers, a constellation is a group of stars that are connected together to form a figure. Discover their history and how they originated.

title: Ancient Aliens: Russias Secret Files
description: Russia is the home of cosmism, a belief that human civilisation originated in the cosmos and is destined to return to space. But many believe the rise of communism led to a wall of secrecy surrounding extraterrestrial contact in Russia.

title: How The Earth Was Made: Krakatoa
description: The unique geological conditions that make Krakatoa and its successor, Anak Krakatau, extraordinarily explosive and, despite its remoteness, dangerous are explained.

title: Search For The Lost Giants: Into The Bone Cave
description: Chasing accounts of giant skeleton discoveries, Jim and Bill Vieira follow in the footsteps of Abraham Lincoln, who was fascinated by tales and legends of ancient colossi.

title: Evolve: Guts
description: Documentaries on human evolution, neanderthals, primates, and the history of life on earth in general.

title: Looting History: Stealing Beauty: The Morgantina Goddess...
description: ...and The Getty Museum: Curator of the J. Paul Getty Museum�s antiquities collection, Marion True, is in disgrace. Her downfall is brought about by jet-setting antiquities dealer, Robin Symes, and his lover and business partner, shipping heir Christo Michaelides.

title: Mystery Places: Episode 10
description: Visit a UFO house in Taiwan, the US Air Force aircraft and missile storage and maintenance facility in Tucson, Arizona, then travel to Laos, where settlers use war ammunition as everyday objects.

title: The Curse Of Civil War Gold: Overboard
description: Treasure hunters Rick and Marty are on the trail of Civil War gold allegedly confiscated from Jefferson Davis in 1865. Part of it lies at the bottom of Lake Michigan, another in a warren of tunnels beneath Michigan, and another in a cave in Utah.

title: American Pickers: Evel Empire
description: From a Michigan man who was there, Mike learns about Evel Knievels rocket-powered Snake Canyon jump - and is determined to buy a one-of-a-kind billboard rescued from the site.

title: Pawn Stars: Atomic Pawn
description: Chum goes for a hole-in-one when a signed Jack Nicklaus golf glove swings into the shop. Meanwhile, Corey targets a G.I. Joe Tomahawk helicopter toy. Will he get to be a real American hero, or will this deal go AWOL?

title: The Proof Is Out There: Modern Day Dinosaur Sighting, Mysterious Lights...
description: ...Above Norway, and Girl Punches Down Tree: Did a film crew discover proof of a dinosaur living in the African Congo? Are reports of the strange lights in Norway a sign of extraterrestrial activity? And has NASA uncovered proof of an alien structure on an asteroid?

title: Ancient Aliens: The Top Ten Scariest Encounters
description: Ancient Aliens is counting down the top ten scariest encounters that just might be evidence of extraterrestrial visitation. From an encounter in rural Texas that left onlookers with unexplainable injuries, to mysterious cattle mutilations.

title: Forged In Fire: Gladiators of the Forge: The Battles Continue
description: In the second episode, its back to the Forged in Fire Gladiators Arena for two more ferocious one-on-one battles. Our current champion won two rounds and has a chance to win the greatest prize ever awarded in the Forge: $75,000.

title: Mystery Places: Episode 11
description: Discover incredible facts about the Nauru Island, observe the daily life of a garbage collector in Brazil, visit a cave village in China, and take a closer look at the working conditions of a man who works in the Egyptian desert.

title: The Curse Of Civil War Gold: All That Glitters
description: Treasure hunters Rick and Marty are on the trail of Civil War gold allegedly confiscated from Jefferson Davis in 1865. Part of it lies at the bottom of Lake Michigan, another in a warren of tunnels beneath Michigan, and another in a cave in Utah.

title: American Pickers: The Great Razooly
description: Flying solo, Mike heads to the California castle home of the Great Razooly - a sculptor, entrepreneur, and horror icon whose one-of-a-kind collection includes monsters, gargoyles, and a custom rocket ship on the front lawn.

title: Pawn Stars: Bohemian Pawnsody
description: When Rick gets a chance at an iconic collection of Hard Rock photographs, can he capture a deal, or will another one bite the dust? Next, Corey gets revved up for a Harley Davidson motor. Will he put the pedal to the metal, or stop short?

title: Commando Missions: Heraklion Operation
description: In the north of Crete, six commandos land in a cove. On this island that has been occupied for two years, they have been given a high-risk mission�to infiltrate the Heraklion airfield to destroy the Luftwaffe bombers and fighter planes.

title: WWII Battles In Colour: Blitzkrieg
description: It took only six weeks for the Nazi Army to conquer France, with an onslaught of tanks, aircraft and German troops. Witness the extraordinary military success of the Blitzkrieg campaign, through rare footage and firsthand accounts.

title: Forged In Fire: Gladiators Of The Forge: Viking Vs Gladiator
description: The defending champion has taken down two opponents, including a two-time Gladiator of the Forge. Now our champions sights are set on a new challenger and a new weapon, a Gladiator favourite - the deadly Sica.

title: Bermuda Triangle: Into Cursed Waters: Bermuda Triangles First Blood
description: The team investigates a large wooden shipwreck that could be one of the earliest victims: the long-lost SS D.H. Mount. Six months after the Civil War, the Mount departed New York with 22 pro-Union politicians.

title: Bermuda Triangle: Into Cursed Waters: Pirates in the Caribbean
description: Are modern-day pirates prowling the Bermuda Triangle in search of victims? The team takes on the twisted case of a missing luxury boat called the Saba Bank lost in the vicinity of the Bermuda Triangle in 1974.

title: Bermuda Triangle: Into Cursed Waters: Graveyard Of The Atlantic
description: The team has secret intel on a wreck that might be a legendary 1930s disappearance: the champion racing yacht, Ingomar.

title: Bermuda Triangle: Into Cursed Waters: Falling Stars
description: Two British passenger planes, nearly identical, named the Star Tiger and the Star Ariel vanished in the 1940s. They disappear one year apart, nearly to the day.

title: Bermuda Triangle: Into Cursed Waters: Eye Of The Cyclops
description: The team has a chance to solve the case of the USS Cyclops. Missing since 1918 with 309 sailors, this 500-foot freighter represents the single deadliest Bermuda Triangle loss.

title: Bermuda Triangle: Into Cursed Waters: Bermuda Triangles Greatest Mysteries
description: The team unveils the greatest mysteries of the Bermuda Triangle: its most perplexing vanished ships and planes, and the strange and powerful forces said to be behind the Triangles reputation.

title: Forged In Fire: Beat The Judges: Shamshir Showdown
description: In this final "Beat the Judges" competition, two former Forged in Fire champions duel it out in a 5-hour round, making a pichangatti. With only 8 hours to produce the intimidating shamshir, will this champion have what it takes to beat a judge?

title: Forged In Fire: Beat the Unbeaten: Off the Hook
description: Two previous champions will face off in a gruelling 5-hour challenge, making a blade inspired by Hollywood for the chance to duke it out against one of our titans of the forge. Will either of these smiths have what it takes to Beat the Unbeaten?

title: Lost Relics of the Knights Templar: Reliquary Box
description: The series finale focuses on the reliquary casket. Carl and Hamilton know the casket dates to a later period - probably early 15th century. Yet a series of engravings on it - the box code - appears to make veiled references to Templar beliefs.

title: Lost Relic Hunters: The First Crusade
description: Carl and Hamilton investigate a Crusader sword and helmet that date back more than 900 years. Then, travelling to Italy�s floating city, they learn more about how and why Venice adopted St Mark as its patron saint.

title: Bupkis: The Picture
description: Pete finds himself obsessing over a photograph of himself online that an apparent internet troll has been posting. Pete ends up on a dark path as he tries to hunt down the anonymous troll, leading his mother Amy to try to protect him from himself.

title: Two And A Half Men: I Changed My Mind About The Milk
description: Waldens proposal on Zoeys birthday does not go as planned. Jake adjusts to life in the military and Alan is on edge because any permanent relationship between Walden and Zoey will lead to his eviction from the house.

title: Two And A Half Men: A Big Bag Of Dog
description: Shortly after his break up with Zoey, Walden has a breakdown And becomes irritable. After a slight intervention, Walden gets over it And gets even with Zoey by getting her daughter a large slobbering dog for her birthday.

title: Two And A Half Men: Four Balls, Two Bats And One Mitt
description: Alan and Lyndsey decide to progress their relationship further by having a pair of threesomes. The first one will involve Walden, the second one a woman of Alans choice.

title: Two And A Half Men: You Do Know What The Lollipop Is For
description: Missi, an old family friend comes to visit for a week and develops a relationship with Jake who is home on leave from the Army. When Jake comes to return to base though, Missi reveals she already has a boyfriend.

title: Two And A Half Men: Thats Not What They Call It In Amsterdam
description: Walden starts dating Rose. This news shocks Alan and he tries to warn Walden about Rose, describing her tactics and history with Charlie, but Walden disregards them as Rose explained everything to him.

title: Two And A Half Men: Ferrets, Attack!
description: Walden asks Rose to move in so they can spend more time together. The next day, however, Walden gets a call from Zoey. They meet and Zoey confesses she still loves him, which forces Walden into making a decision.

title: Two And A Half Men: Avoid The Chinese Mustard
description: Walden hires an actress to play the part of his girlfriend and ends up falling for her. Meanwhile, Jake and Missi plan a rendezvous which doesnt go well when Alan is informed that Jake went AWOL from the Army.

title: Two And A Half Men: Something My Gynecologist Said
description: Lyndsey asks Alan for a commitment, which he doesnt take lightly. Walden is picked up by a rich older woman, who sees him as a poverty-stricken love toy, and she takes him back to her place and seduces him.

title: Two And A Half Men: I Scream When I Pee
description: Alan finds himself in a bind when his beautiful ex-wife makes a pass at him. However, being in a committed relationship with Lyndsey, Alan tries to do the right thing by turning down Kandi and telling Lyndsey. Meanwhile, Walden helps Berta celebrate her birthday.

title: Two And A Half Men: One Nut Johnson
description: Tired of dating or even meeting women who are only interested in his fortune, Walden decides to create an online persona as a poor schlub named Sam Wilson who is very much like Alan Harper (no job, no prospects, no charm). Then he meets Kate, a wannabe fashion designer.

title: Two And A Half Men: Give Santa A Tail-Hole
description: Still pretending to be the poverty-stricken "Sam Wilson", Walden spends Christmas with Kate. Meanwhile, Walden And Billy close a deal to sell their electronic suitcase for $1.2 billion. Elsewhere, Alans Christmas goes south when all his loved ones have other commitments.

title: Two And A Half Men: Welcome To Alancrest
description: Walden wants to invest in his girlfriend Kates fashion career, without her discovering that he is billionaire Walden Schmidt rather than broke "Sam Wilson", as hes led her to believe. What is more, the stress of the deception is beginning to affect Waldens health.

title: Two And A Half Men: Grab A Feather And Get In Line
description: Fed up with his double-life and feeling that Kate might be the one, Walden decides he should throw away his "Sam Wilson" alias and confess to who he really is. Kates in New York at a fashion show, so Walden, accompanied by Alan, set off to tell her the truth in person.

title: Two And A Half Men: Run, Steven Staven! Run!
description: Lyndseys miffed that she doesnt have a key to the beach house. Meanwhile, Walden, Alan, Billy and Herb share stories about women.

title: Two And A Half Men: Paint It, Pierce It Or Plug It
description: Jake brings home his 36-year-old girlfriend Tammy but Alan becomes concerned about her and Jake due to her job as a tattoo artist, her kids and time spent in prison.

title: Two And A Half Men: Advantage: Fat, Flying Baby
description: Valentines day is approaching and Alan wants to make it special for Lyndsey. Unfortunately, his plans go awry at the last minute. Kate is back in town and wants to meet up with Walden but can he convince her to take him back?

title: Two And A Half Men: Throgwarten Middle School Mysteries

title: Two And A Half Men: The 9:04 Pemberton

title: Two And A Half Men: Big Episode: Someone Stole A Spoon
description: Walden and Alan try to cheer up a lonely Herb, but end up living it up a little too large.

title: Miss You Can Do It
description: Diagnosed with cerebral palsy at age two, Abbey Curran became the first woman with disabilities to compete in the Miss USA Pageant. This documentary highlights the extraordinary work Curran is doing with the pageant she founded specifically for girls with special needs.

title: Amy Schumer: Live At The Apollo
description: Comedy superstar Amy Schumer brings her unique blend of honesty and an unapologetic sense of humour in this stand-up special from the historic Apollo Theatre in New York City.

title: The Boring Life of Jacqueline: The Blog
description: Suzanne suggests that Jacqueline start a blog.

title: Entourage: The Scene
description: Pre-production on "Queens Boulevard" is moving along nicely and famed indie director Billy Walsh is tapped to helm the project. Vince takes an immediate liking to Walsh but Eric has concerns, especially when he discovers Walsh has added one particular certain scene.

title: Entourage: New York
description: Tired of being known as "Vinces guy", Eric wants a title commensurate with his duties. With his latest shoot taking him to New York, Vince prepares to say goodbye to L.A. Drama considers his next role while Turtle stakes out a claim as Vinces farewell party promoter.

title: Enlightened: No Doubt
description: In the hope she will drop her crusade against Abaddonn, Tyler gets Eileen to arrange a meeting for Amy with Szidon. Dougie goes off the rails after getting official word about Cogentivas future, while Amy confides in Krista about the Abaddonn expose.

title: Enlightened: Agent Of Change
description: On the precipice of bringing down Abaddonn, Amy warns Tyler to prepare himself for the inevitable fallout. When Szidon gets wind of her intentions, Amy wrongly points a finger at Krista, who has just given birth.

title: Banshee: Armies Of One
description: When Jasons past catches up to him, Lucas decides to make a deal in order to save the boys life, and maybe his own. In the absence of Carrie, Gordon and Devas lives spin out of control. Proctor teaches Rebecca a hard lesson in allegiance.

title: Game Of Thrones: Baelor
description: With Sansas life in danger, Ned makes a fateful decision. Robb wins his first major victory and captures a prized prisoner. As Drogos wound festers, Dany defies Qotho and puts her trust in the witch Mirri Maz Duur.

title: Game Of Thrones: Fire And Blood
description: Season finale. As tragic news spreads across the Seven Kingdoms, Bran and Rickon share a prophetic dream, Catelyn interrogates Jaime about her sons fall, Robbs destiny is forever changed and a new king rises.

description: Problems grow between Shaima and Hassan, and Shaimaas mother, Rabeaa, is frustrated. Meanwhile, Shoaib discovers a shocking truth about an old familys secret.

title: Asher Safha: Episode 4
description: Najms secret about an old love widens the gap between him and his wife. Later, Salem is waiting in prison for his release to freedom.

title: Asher Safha: Episode 5

description: Hanan cancels her engagement party because of her love for Fahd, and Salma finds herself in a difficult situation because of that, so she tries to find out the reasons in her own way.

title: Asher Safha: Episode 9

title: Asher Safha: Episode 10

description: Rashid suffers from a health crisis and is taken to the hospital, later the two families meet during their visit to Rashid and a shocking confrontation occurs.

title: Asher Safha: Episode 27
description: Hanan suffers in her married life with Fahd, and Khawla and Salems mother discover a shocking matter that Salem has caused. When Fai notices great changes on Najem, she asks him to provide an explanation for her questions.

title: Asher Safha: Episode 28
description: When a Najems wife confronts Salma about their relationship, you wont expect Salmas response. Hanan is disappointed When Fahd has a baby.

title: Asher Safha: Episode 29
description: It is the day that Salma must face everyone for herself and her old love. Later, Hanan leaves Fahds house, but an unexpected event makes her return to him.

title: Asher Safha: Episode 30
description: Rabea manages to take revenge on Nawal and Rashid, and Salma finishes the novel she started previousley, will she fulfill her wishes?

title: Dehbash: Episode 1
description: When a deaf girl survives the sinking of a merchant boat off the coast, Al-Tawash Abu Saud helps her and secretly marries her.

title: Dehbash: Episode 2
description: Despite his wifes suspicions, Al-Tawash has a child with his deaf new wife Shamma, but things dont go as expected when it becomes clear that their child has disabilities.

title: Dehbash: Episode 3
description: After twenty years, Dahbash decides to return to Kuwait with his father and mother. Over the years, Shamma still strugling with her son, who has grown up with a mental disability.

title: Dehbash: Episode 4
description: When Sheikh Saleh arrives in Kuwait, he meets Dahbash and his parents and tries to help them.

title: Dehbash: Episode 5
description: Al-Tawash and his cousin are quarreling over their grandparents property, especially the familys house on the beach.

title: Dehbash: Episode 6
description: When George (the Muslim American) arrives in Kuwait, it is up to Saleh to take him under his wing and teach him the Arabic language and Quran with Dahbash and Shammas son.

title: Dehbash: Episode 7
description: Al-Tawash asks one of his freinds to find Shammas Son a job, and his cousin hires him without knowing that he is al-Tawashs son.

title: Dehbash: Episode 8
description: Because of the dispute between Al-Tawash and his cousin Abu Mubarak, Abdullah Shammas son is fired from his job, so Sheikh Saleh intervenes when he suggests that George work in his place.

title: Dehbash: Episode 9
description: While competition increases between the cousins merchants, in the old quarter, Al-Dahbash and Abdullah are still subsisting from their daily lives.

title: Dehbash: Episode 10
description: When a child laborer in a market is kidnapped by merchants, tensions rise in the market.

title: Dehbash: Episode 11
description: For twenty years, Al-Tawashs first wife was ignorant of her stepson, but everything changes when she begins to have doubts. Later, Bilal and Abdullah see strange dreams, and they visit Sheikh Saleh to interpret the dream.

title: Dehbash: Episode 12
description: George, who is called Bilal now, approaches Shamma and her son, and the Al-Tawash group becomes increasingly suspicious, and they plot conspiracies to entrap him.

title: Dehbash: Episode 13
description: When Bilal is expelled from his place of residence, he turns to Abu Mubarak, but the problems will not end with his move.Meanwhile, Moza becomes increasingly suspicious that the Tawash has a son.

title: Dehbash: Episode 14
description: Dahbash decides to take a career in diving and begins to learn swimming at one of the narrators whom Sheikh Saleh introduced him to.

title: Dehbash: Episode 15
description: Bilal teaches Shamma and her son the sign language that he had learned in his country, but when the Al-Tawash freinds learns of his frequent visits to Shammas house, they tell Al-Tawash of this.

title: Dehbash: Episode 16
description: Dahbash becomes able to dive and collect pearls, and one of his diving trips leads him to an amazing discovery that could change his life.

title: Dehbash: Episode 17
description: While Abdullah has disturbing nightmares, Dahbashs financial status gets better when he buys a boat of his own.

title: Dehbash: Episode 18
description: Bilal gets into trouble in a market, but things are turned upside down when the truth is revealed.

title: Dehbash: Episode 19
description: Bilal realizes that Sheikh Salah has testified in his favour. Meanwhile, the incident causes one of the merchant to dig into Bilals past and secrets.

title: Dehbash: Episode 20
description: News leaks out about the problem that Bilal caused before he came to Kuwait. Meanwile, Bilal knows that someone will bring him back to Bahrain.
